Introduction

Park Junseo is a South Korean dancer and singer under PocketDol Studio. He is a member of the boy group BAE173.

In 2016, he was a member and contestant of the pre-debut survival group and show BOYS24, but was sadly eliminated and couldn't make it into the final group.

On September 21, 2020, Park Junseo was introduced as the eighth member of BAE173, with whom he debuted on November 19, 2020 with the release of the mini album "Intersection: Spark".

On September 26, 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7, which started in October 2024. He was eliminated in the final after ranking 21st place.
